{"type": "article", "id": 4411, "title": "Meet The Wicker 橱柜与收纳装置", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-16T08:17:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233104VIw5Cng8R2WNOtoX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰埃因霍恩设计学院（Design Academy Eindhoven）的两位毕业生 Jasmina Grase 与 Nils Chudy 组成了一个设计二人组，携手来自拉脱维亚的工匠，运用了传统的柳条材质进行编织，结合工业金属的框架，设计出来了一系列极具当代设计风格的橱柜与收纳装置 <a href=\"http://www.meetthewicker.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Meet The Wicker</a>，力图表现出一种手作与工艺结合的美感。如需购买，请联系 we@chudyandgrase.com。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233102uib16SEDv0atXHWx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233102xJyipzqPcXQVtkgj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523310341AJON9WYa8dclBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233103HLZSDmMyu1VPsxXG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}